{"tid":931424,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大律師公會前主席林定國　獲委消委會主席","createTime":"2018-12-07T04:37:09.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-07T05:49:33.000Z","uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"c9e76e74024b46a9492215b3f2c259ba4be11456","tid":931424,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-07T04:37:09.000Z","msg":"政府今日公布委任資深大律師、大律師公會前主席林定國為消費者委員會（消委會）主席，任期兩年，由2019年1月1日起生效。<br />\n<br />\n林定國2017年出任大律師公會主席，在今年初改選時連任失敗，輸給戴啟思。<br />\n<br />\n林定國是接替已出任消委會主席六年的黃玉山。<br />\n<br />\n政府發言人說：「林先生對公共服務竭誠盡心，經驗豐富，我們相信他定能繼續領導消委會推動香港的消費者權益。」「我們非常感謝黃教授多年來對消委會作出的傑出貢獻，他的熱誠投入和領導對消委會維護消費者權益的工作至為重要。」<br />\n<br />\n政府亦宣布委任何聞達、林凱章、林建康、雷紹麟、雷永昌和溫麗司，以及再度委任林新強、林詩棋和黃紹基為消委會委員，任期兩年，由2019年1月1日起生效。<br />\n<br />\n陳文宜、陳淑芳、梁少康、李健虎、沈孝欣及黃錦輝則於2018年12月31日完成任期後離任。<br />\n<br />\n由2019年1月1日起，消委會委員名單如下：<br />\n<br />\n主席：林定國資深大律師<br />\n<br />\n副主席：陳家殷<br />\n<br />\n委員：<br />\n陳靜芬資深大律師<br />\n陳錦榮<br />\n霍偉棟博士<br />\n馮丹媚<br />\n何俊賢<br />\n何聞達<br />\n徐晉暉<br />\n鄺祖盛<br />\n林凱章<br />\n林建康<br />\n林新強<br />\n林詩棋<br />\n劉子芸<br />\n李泳蘭<br />\n雷紹麟<br />\n雷永昌醫生<br />\n蕭景威<br />\n譚鳳儀教授<br />\n黃紹基<br />\n溫麗司 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E5%A4%A7%E5%BE%8B%E5%B8%AB%E5%85%AC%E6%9C%83%E5%89%8D%E4%B8%BB%E5%B8%AD%E6%9E%97%E5%AE%9A%E5%9C%8B-%E7%8D%B2%E5%A7%94%E6%B6%88%E5%A7%94%E6%9C%83%E4%B8%BB%E5%B8%AD/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%25BE%258B%25E5%25B8%25AB%25E5%2585%25AC%25E6%259C%2583%25E5%2589%258D%25E4%25B8%25BB%25E5%25B8%25AD%25E6%259E%2597%25E5%25AE%259A%25E5%259C%258B-%25E7%258D%25B2%25E5%25A7%2594%25E6%25B6%2588%25E5%25A7%2594%25E6%259C%2583%25E4%25B8%25BB%25E5%25B8%25AD%2F&d=KSHrbrcZAjs90lyxCGdwe5ZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=45ae7ecd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%25BE%258B%25E5%25B8%25AB%25E5%2585%25AC%25E6%259C%2583%25E5%2589%258D%25E4%25B8%25BB%25E5%25B8%25AD%25E6%259E%2597%25E5%25AE%259A%25E5%259C%258B-%25E7%258D%25B2%25E5%25A7%2594%25E6%25B6%2588%25E5%25A7%2594%25E6%259C%2583%25E4%25B8%25BB%25E5%25B8%25AD%2F&h=bfda1666\" target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E5%A4%A7%E5%BE%8B%E5%B8%AB%E5%85%AC%E6%9C%83%E5%89%8D%E4%B8%BB%E5%B8%AD%E6%9E%97%E5%AE%9A%E5%9C%8B-%E7%8D%B2%E5%A7%94%E6%B6%88%E5%A7%94%E6%9C%83%E4%B8%BB%E5%B8%AD/</a>"},{"pid":"d02a3f8956efefc3b2d7e88aa63ba4aa1907e648","tid":931424,"uid":205462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-07T04:54:42.000Z","msg":"其實委任咁多人入去，有乜實際用處呢? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"384ed3d44454b32f00ab4c6dccfc5950d4578d81","tid":931424,"uid":137569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-07T04:59:44.000Z","msg":"都係任由商家千鳩小市民"},{"pid":"09636485c6ca0e00abc80fd94ad515202d736551","tid":931424,"uid":61589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d02a3f8956efefc3b2d7e88aa63ba4aa1907e648","tid":931424,"uid":205462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-07T04:54:42.000Z","msg":"其實委任咁多人入去，有乜實際用處呢? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-07T05:49:33.000Z","msg":"個個月逗緊十幾廿萬人工架大佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}